{{Top|leg}}
'''Coruscant civilian transports''' were small freighters used by the citizens of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] to get to other areas of a city, or another part of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. They could each hold a fair amount of people, and were usually piloted by only one or two pilots. They were outfitted with light armor plating, to protect from heavy damage in the event of a crash.

